data.text: @enews As if the Duchess of Cambridge was going to mother markle!! She is having a baby and 2 others to look after. markle is a big girl, she can look after herself

@enews I wish people would stop referring to Cate's surname as 'Middleton' still. Her official title now she is married is Catherine Mountbatten-Windsor, Duchess of Cambridge and her name is spelt with a C not a K! Anyone with access to google would be able to find this, like I have.
